OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fmostly clearing to leave clear skies
OL,7,Fthrough the evening and overnight.
OL,8,FCloud building in the early hours,
OL,9,Fwith blustery showers arriving by dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,12,Fscattered blustery showers. The
OL,13,Fshowers turning heavy at times with
OL,14,Fthe odd rumble of thunder and hail.
OL,15,FFeeling cool, especially in the wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
